---
title: Double Sweet-Sticky Crispy Chicken & Garlic Rice with Pear Slaw & Japanese Mayo
description: Sweetly glazed chicken bites are popping with flavour in a bowl that’s already got the aromas of garlic rice. If that still isn’t enough, a Japanese mayo may be the thing to tick all your tasty boxes. We’ll let you give it a try and find out!

